"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Tutorial\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://oceanwp.org/?p=624466\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1338:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-translate-oceanwp-woocommerce-store/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/how-to-translate-oceanwp-woocommerce-store.png\" width=\"1200\" height=\"700\" title=\"How to Translate Your OceanWP and WooCommerce Store (the Quick Way)\" alt=\"How to Translate Your OceanWP and WooCommerce Store (the Quick Way)\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">Translating a website used to be time-consuming and expensive. But with a multilingual-ready theme like OceanWP and WPML’s new Translate Everything mode, you can automatically translate your entire store in a fraction of the time, even on the tightest budget. See how it all works in this tutorial video: Why You Should Translate Your WooCommerce [&#8230;]<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-translate-oceanwp-woocommerce-store/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Allison Rivers\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10268:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-translate-oceanwp-woocommerce-store/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/how-to-translate-oceanwp-woocommerce-store.png\" width=\"1200\" height=\"700\" title=\"How to Translate Your OceanWP and WooCommerce Store (the Quick Way)\" alt=\"How to Translate Your OceanWP and WooCommerce Store (the Quick Way)\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>Translating a website used to be time-consuming and expensive. But with a multilingual-ready theme like OceanWP and WPML’s new <strong>Translate Everything</strong> mode, you can automatically translate your entire store in a fraction of the time, even on the tightest budget.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>See how it all works in this tutorial video:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<p class=\"responsive-video-wrap clr\"><iframe title=\"How to translate your OceanWP website with WPML (The quick and easy way)\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GxyPFzK634Q?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Why You Should Translate Your WooCommerce Store</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Thanks to continuous improvements in automatic translation, translating your online store can be one of the easiest ways to grow your business.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Reach New Customers</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We all know ranking highly in search results draws in more customers. When you translate your site, you make it possible to <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/multilingual-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">rank well in search results for multiple languages</a>. Without changing any of your products, conducting costly research, or increasing your ad spend, you can reach a whole new market.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Increase Sales</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once a potential customer lands on your site and finds the products they’re looking for, it’s important to make it easy to complete their purchase. Having a fully-translated checkout process reduces the chance of cart abandonment. More completed sales = more money in your bottom line.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Improve Trust</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When customers find a company they can trust, they come back again and again. Providing services and products in a person’s native language demonstrates an interest and willingness to engage with them. Continuing to provide after-purchase support in the form of translated documentation can be the difference between a one-time purchaser and a lifelong customer and advocate.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best Tools for Translating Your Online Store Easily and Affordably</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To get your online store up and running as soon as possible, be sure to use tools that allow you to build and translate your store quickly and easily. When you build a WooCommerce store using WPML and OceanWP, you can rest assured that everything will work as it should. This is thanks to WPML and OceanWP’s commitment to ongoing compatibility.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>OceanWP &#8211; A Theme That’s Multilingual-Ready</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to translate your site, it’s important to use a multilingual-ready theme like OceanWP. Multilingual-ready means you can translate every part of the theme, from <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/build-multilingual-wordpress-sites-using-oceanwp-theme-and-wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">pages, menus, and widgets</a>, to the <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/build-multilingual-wordpress-sites-using-oceanwp-theme-and-wpml/oceanwp-extensions-compatibility-wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">many extensions you can use to customize your WooCommerce store</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1.translated-store-1024x576.png\" alt=\"translate woocommerce store\" class=\"wp-image-624468\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1.translated-store-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1.translated-store-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1.translated-store-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1.translated-store-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1.translated-store.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /><figcaption><em>A translated online store built with OceanWP</em></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h3>WPML &#8211; Translate Your Whole Site Automatically</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wpml.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPML</a> is the most popular WordPress plugin for multilingual sites, and for good reason! The new <strong>Translate Everything</strong> mode, introduced in their latest release, allows you to:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Automatically translate your entire site in minutes;</li><li>Review the automatic translations yourself or hire a reviewer to make sure they sound natural and accurate;</li><li>Effortlessly keep your site’s translations up to date (they update automatically any time you edit your default content);</li><li>Choose from Google Translate, Microsoft Azure, or DeepL to power automatic translation;</li><li>Translate content created with page builders like Elementor.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/2.translating-site-automatically-1024x576.png\" alt=\"translate woocommerce store\" class=\"wp-image-624469\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/2.translating-site-automatically-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/2.translating-site-automatically-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/2.translating-site-automatically-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/2.translating-site-automatically-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/2.translating-site-automatically.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /><figcaption><em>Sit back and relax as WPML automatically translates your site</em></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Although automatic translation isn’t completely free, WPML gets great discounts from automatic translation providers due to the high volume they translate every month. They then pass along those discounts directly to you. This means automatic translation is super affordable for even the most budget-conscious.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, with WPML, your translations are saved to your own database, not another plugin’s cloud. You own your translations yourself.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>WooCommerce Multilingual &#8211; Translate Your Products and Add Multi-Currency Support</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>WooCommerce Multilingual is a free add-on plugin that comes with the purchase of a WPML Multilingual CMS or Agency account.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It allows you to translate:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Products</li><li>Product attributes</li><li>Product variations</li><li>Cart and checkout pages</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8230;and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3.translation-options-for-products-1024x575.png\" alt=\"translate woocommerce site\" class=\"wp-image-624470\" width=\"768\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3.translation-options-for-products-1024x575.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3.translation-options-for-products-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3.translation-options-for-products-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3.translation-options-for-products-1536x863.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3.translation-options-for-products.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /><figcaption><em>Deciding how to translate products in WCML’s setup wizard</em></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>It also includes robust <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/related-projects/woocommerce-multilingual/multi-currency-support-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">multi-currency features</a> so you can display different currencies based on language or location. Plus, you can set exchange rates, custom shipping rates, and configure different payment gateways per currency.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4.multi-currency-settings-1024x576.png\" alt=\"translate woocommerce store\" class=\"wp-image-624471\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4.multi-currency-settings-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4.multi-currency-settings-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4.multi-currency-settings-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4.multi-currency-settings-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4.multi-currency-settings.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /><figcaption><em>Setting different currencies per language</em></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Get Started with WPML</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Start translating your WooCommerce store today with WPML and WooCommerce Multilingual. A <a href=\"https://wpml.org/purchase/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPML Multilingual CMS or Agency account</a> includes everything you need to translate your entire site automatically and get your multilingual business up and running!</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-translate-oceanwp-woocommerce-store/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-translate-oceanwp-woocommerce-store/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n\n\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:8:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"How to Create a Dynamic Appointment Website with OceanWP &amp; Crocoblock\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0: