round-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Lior Zelering\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2374:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/nothing-can-stop-oceanwp-movement/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/oceanwp-moves-ahead.png\" width=\"1200\" height=\"657\" title=\"Nothing Can Stop the OceanWP Movement\" alt=\"Nothing Can Stop the OceanWP Movement\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>Hello everyone,<br>As you well know, in the last two years, OceanWP has gone through tremendous growth.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>During this time, we launched our new Vanilla version, added 150 new demos and some theme features, launched the Gutenberg blocks and also fixed many old issues and improved the theme’s performance, styling, etc.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We have a long product road-map ahead and are excited about the years to come!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As we continued to invest in development and support, a former contributor has stepped down.<br>It was brought to our attention that this individual, along with another person, who was dismissed from the team earlier this year, have started a competing project &#8211; we wish them the best of luck.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Unfortunately, we are seeing that these individuals are engaging in a social media attack, unlawfully utilizing access to OceanWP users, and spreading misinformation and scare tactics.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While we take things into legal consideration, we want to assure you that OceanWP remains committed to its users and products.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We thank you for your support and understanding!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please feel free to contact us for any questions or concerns you may have.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>And a NEW FB group is born!</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please join us in our <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/oceanwptheme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">new OceanWP Official Community on Facebook</a> for support, tips, news, and much more&#8230;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/nothing-can-stop-oceanwp-movement/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/nothing-can-stop-oceanwp-movement/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data