ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Colin Newcomer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40297:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/top-16-free-wordpress-live-chat-plugins/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image.jpeg\" width=\"999\" height=\"667\" title=\"The Top 16 Free WordPress Live Chat Plugins\" alt=\"The Top 16 Free WordPress Live Chat Plugins\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>Businesses grow when they find reliable ways to provide an excellent <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/service/what-is-customer-experience\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">customer experience</a> and gain more qualified leads, conversions, and sales.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In 2021, using a live chat service on your website is a quick way to boost your <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/sales/growth-strategy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">business growth</a>, as <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://econsultancy.com/consumers-prefer-live-chat-for-customer-service-stats/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">79% of customers</a> favor live chat over other support channels.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you know that <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://www.emarketer.com/Article/How-Helpful-Live-Chat/1007235\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">38% of customers</a> are more likely to purchase from businesses with <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/service/customers-want-live-chat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">live chat</a> support systems?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, it can be nerve-racking to choose the best option for your website from several free WordPress live chat plugins.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep reading to learn:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Why your business can benefit from having live chat support on your website</li><li>The 16 best free WordPress live chat plugins to choose from</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Benefits of Adding a Live Chat Option to Your WordPress Website</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Live chat solutions have several advantages for your business.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding a WordPress (WP) live chat support plugin to your website will empower you to:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Provide an Excellent Customer Experience</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When customers visit your website, they want quick help and guidance.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://www.pwc.com/us/en/services/consulting/library/consumer-intelligence-series/future-of-customer-experience.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PwC</a>, friendly and knowledgeable help are among the most important aspects of customer experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>An efficient way to provide a better customer experience while saving time and answering objections is by adding live chat support to your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The majority of free WordPress live chat plugins allow multiple conversations to improve customer satisfaction.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreso, these plugins enable real-time problem solving, making it easier to deliver solutions to the right customers when they need them.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Gain Consumers’ Trust and Loyalty</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/us/products/applications/commerce/atg/cross-channel-commerce-survey-333315.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Oracle</a>, 90% of customers claim live chat gives them confidence because they know they’ll get help in real-time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Essentially, having live chat support on your WordPress website will build <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/customers/3-ways-to-delight-your-customers-to-earn-their-trust\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">customers’ trust</a> in your brand. When visitors get a live chat experience on your website, they’re more likely to return and make a purchase.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll earn your website visitors’ trust and gain a competitive edge in your industry through <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/marketing-personalization-examples\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">personalized chats</a>, prompt responses, and the helpful answers you provide.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Boost Website Conversions and Sales</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>By guiding website guests through their journey from the time they land on your website, you will help them make quick buying decisions, shortening the <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/sales/speed-up-sales-cycle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sales cycle</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using advanced targeted trigger options will help you reduce the sales abandonment rate and increase conversions and sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.emarketer.com/Article/How-Helpful-Live-Chat/1007235\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Studies</a> have shown that more people buy from companies that provide a live chat experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Live chat also empowers you to create answers to common questions. When you make these preset answers, you’re able to provide <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/service/proactive-customer-service\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">proactive support</a>, better engagement, and quick response time, ultimately boosting conversions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With targeted messages and proactive triggers through WordPress live chat plugins, you’ll turn a user from a website visitor to a potential